Medical Questions
questions.question_description: The best way for me to quote you accurately is to discuss all of your current and past medical information. To guide us through this process, I’ll ask you a series of pre-qualifying questions. Once you apply for the coverage, we will complete the underwriting process and review your medical history and prescriptions. Please take your time to understand and accurately answer these questions so nothing is overlooked.
